e that the status property may also be used to indicate that a concept is deprecated</td></tr><tr><td>retirementDate</td><td>retirementDate</td><td>http://hl7.org/fhir/concept-properties#retirementDate</td><td>dateTime</td><td>The date at which a concept was retired</td></tr><tr><td>finess</td><td>finess</td><td>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/concept-properties#finess</td><td>boolean</td><td>Permet de définir les codes concepts utilisés par FINESS+</td></tr></table><p><b>Concepts</b></p><p>This case-insensitive code system <code>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/CodeSystem/tre-r366-type-objet</code> defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>dateValid</b></td><td><b>dateMaj</b></td><td><b>status</b></td><td><b>finess</b></td><td><b>French (France) (fr)</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">AC<a name=\"tre-r366-type-objet-AC\"> </a></td><td>Activité</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td><td>true</td><td/></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EG<a name=\"tre-r366-type-objet-EG\"> </a></td><td>Entité géographique d'exercice FINESS</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td><td>true</td><td>Entité géographique</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">EN<a name=\"tre-r366-type-objet-EN\"> </a></td><td>Entreprise INSEE</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td><td>true</td><td>Entreprise</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">ET<a name=\"tre-r366-type-objet-ET\"> </a></td><td>Etablissement INSEE</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td><td>true</td><td>Etablissement</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">GR<a name=\"tre-r366-type-objet-GR\"> </a></td><td>Groupement</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td><td>true</td><